《'''特厲鬼屋'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Abattoir'''''}}）是一部2016年美國[[恐怖片|恐怖片]]，由[[戴倫·連恩·布斯曼|戴倫·連恩·布斯曼]]執導，David Schow、Teddy Tenenbaum和Christopher Monfette編劇<ref name="Variety">{{Cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/global/cannes-abbatoir-sequel-dwelling-unveiled-by-versatile-exclusive-1201495935/|title=Cannes: ‘Abattoir’ Sequel ‘Dwelling’ Unveiled by Versatile (EXCLUSIVE)|access-date=2016-09-26|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206151248/https://variety.com/2015/film/global/cannes-abbatoir-sequel-dwelling-unveiled-by-versatile-exclusive-1201495935/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這部片在2016年6月7日於{{link-en|洛杉磯影展|Los Angeles Film Festival}}首映。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://tickets.lafilmfestival.com/Online/default.asp?doWork::WScontent::loadArticle=Load&BOparam::WScontent::loadArticle::article_id=3415F1D1-9153-483F-A351-1048EEE2DE83|title=Abattoir|accessdate=September 10, 2016|work={{noitalic|{{tsl|en|Los Angeles Film Festival||Los Angeles Film Festival}}}}|publisher=Film Independent|archive-date=2016-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161016062350/https://tickets.lafilmfestival.com/Online/default.asp?doWork::WScontent::loadArticle=Load&BOparam::WScontent::loadArticle::article_id=3415F1D1-9153-483F-A351-1048EEE2DE83|dead-url=no}}</ref>

